# Screen Pet - Mental model bat buoc nho

App nay KHONG phai CRUD; no la **mini game engine + Android overlay**.
Moi tinh nang phai dat dung lop trong stack sau:

```
Overlay Service (Foreground + WindowManager TYPE_APPLICATION_OVERLAY)
        |
PetOverlayWindowHost (window kich thuoc sprite, di chuyen theo anchor)
        |
PetOverlayContent / PetPlayField (Compose UI: PetShimeSprite + drag)
        |
PetViewModel / PetOverlayPlaySink (presentation)
        |
TickPetUseCase / DispatchPetInputUseCase / UpdatePlayAreaUseCase (domain)
        |
PetEngine (FSM + physics) <- PetSimulationRepository (SSOT StateFlow)
```

Quy tac vang:
- **SSOT**: `PetSimulationRepository.world: StateFlow<PetWorldState>`. Activity va Service deu doc cung 1 instance (Hilt @Singleton).
- **Tick**: chi 1 nguon tick tai 1 thoi diem. Khi overlay bat -> `PetOverlaySession.active = true` -> `PetViewModel` huy tick, Service chiem; nguoc lai khi tat.
- **Mutex**: moi `tickPetUseCase` / `dispatchPetInputUseCase` phai qua `PetSimulationUpdateMutex` de tranh race giua Activity va Service.
- **Don vi**: anchor/velocity tinh bang **pixel logical cua engine** (khong phai dp). UI vẽ sprite size = `with(density){SPRITE_WIDTH_PX.toDp()}`.

Roadmap on lai khi them tinh nang moi:
1. Pet noi (Service + WindowManager).
2. Sprite animation (frame + cache).
3. Movement (velocity + delta).
4. Drag (cumulative dragAmount, tranh race window di chuyen).
5. State machine (PetRuntimePhase).
6. Random behavior / AI.
7. Physics (gravity, bouncing, edge).

Tu khoa search khi bi: `android overlay kotlin`, `WindowManager TYPE_APPLICATION_OVERLAY`,
`compose ComposeView in service`, `sprite animation kotlin`, `game loop coroutine`, `finite state machine kotlin`.
